        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and the groves, and the carved images and the molten images, he brake in pieces; ordered them to be broken; the groves were statues, or images in groves, and thereby distinguished from those made of wood, and were carved, and from those that were of molten metal, and were placed elsewhere: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and made dust of them, and strewed it upon the graves of them that had sacrificed unto them, see 2 Kings 23:6. ",
